The purpose of this directory is to run Cucumber tests on Catroid.

SETUP:
-------------------------------------------------------------------------------

You can use RVM with the .rvmrc provided in this directory.

Install Ruby (http://www.ruby-lang.org).
Install RVM (optional, https://rvm.io).
Install Cucumber (http://cukes.info).
Install Calabash-Android (https://github.com/calabash/calabash-android).
Install Python (for the run-script, http://www.python.org)

RUNNING TESTS:
-------------------------------------------------------------------------------

python run.py --help


CHANGELOG:
-------------------------------------------------------------------------------

2012-11-28
Initial commit. Added calabash-android skeleton and run-script.
There is only a dummy-test for now.
